<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><?xml-stylesheet href="http://www.blogger.com/styles/atom.css" type="text/css"?><feed xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom' xmlns:openSearch='http://a9.com/-/spec/opensearchrss/1.0/' xmlns:gd="http://schemas.google.com/g/2005"><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post1295579991922375223..comments</id><updated>2020-01-23T03:10:59.197+08:00</updated><title type='text'>Comments on 编程随想的博客: 每周转载：香港“反送中”政治抗议活动大事记（9月初至10月初）</title><link rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#feed' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/feeds/comments/default'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default?start-index=500&amp;max-results=999'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html'/><link rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/"/><link rel='previous' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default?start-index=1&amp;max-results=999'/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='//4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><generator version='7.00' uri='http://www.blogger.com'>Blogger</generator><openSearch:totalResults>520</openSearch:totalResults><openSearch:startIndex>500</openSearch:startIndex><openSearch:itemsPerPage>999</openSearch:itemsPerPage><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6561676183379483850</id><published>2019-10-15T17:01:26.626+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T17:01:26.626+08:00</updated><title type='text'>第一次这么靠前…希望博主能看到…有个愿望…就是博主博客的标头的名人名言感觉都特别的棒！！能不能整个合...</title><content type='html'>第一次这么靠前…希望博主能看到…有个愿望…就是博主博客的标头的名人名言感觉都特别的棒！！能不能整个合集一起放送出来呢？</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/6561676183379483850'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/6561676183379483850'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571130086626#c6561676183379483850' title=''/><author><name>慕容锦</name><uri>https://www.blogger.com/profile/14361493289326170956</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/b16-rounded.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1930612297"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午5:01:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1843156964516491630</id><published>2019-10-15T17:01:10.320+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T17:01:10.320+08:00</updated><title type='text'>说到在香港的世预赛，除了香港国歌《愿荣光归香港》，看台观众嘘沦陷区国歌之外，应该关注一下前来比赛的伊...</title><content type='html'>说到在香港的世预赛，除了香港国歌《愿荣光归香港》，看台观众嘘沦陷区国歌之外，应该关注一下前来比赛的伊朗队。&lt;br /&gt;[url=https://www.foxnews.com/sports/pressure-fifa-punish-iran-gender-discrimination-blue-girl]Pressure on FIFA to punish Iran over gender discrimination builds after &amp;#39;Blue Girl&amp;#39; death[/url]&lt;br /&gt;有一个伊朗女球迷，她的名字叫Sahar Khodayari,因在三月没有被允许去看伊朗队的比赛，还被拘禁六个月，结果以自焚抗议，引起了国际的关注与指责。而伊朗终于在本月的世预赛主场解除了不许女性看球的禁令。&lt;br /&gt;就是这样的自由，在六十多年前失去以后，现在才以人命的代价争取回来。&lt;br /&gt;关于在伊朗被允许进入体育场看比赛的女球迷，有没有人知道她们是否为Sahar(Blue Girl)哀悼？&lt;br /&gt;若没有，极权国家的人的共情感让人心寒。&lt;br /&gt;可以看[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/05/weekly-share-120.html]每周转载：伊朗迷你裙的变迁（值得某些毛粉反思一下）[/url]&lt;br /&gt;西藏自焚的人，印象中已经超过一百，什么也没有换来。CHINAZIA虽然没胆扩张，杀气自己人来丝毫不输。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/1843156964516491630'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/1843156964516491630'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571130070320#c1843156964516491630' title=''/><author><name>地平线</name><uri>http://www.fifa.com</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-896278814"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午5:01:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-196160292738312245</id><published>2019-10-15T16:59:58.129+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:59:58.129+08:00</updated><title type='text'>（接上一单元）&#xa;[b]对台湾动武的可能性[/b]&#xa;包子是否会对台湾动武？&#xa;目前看，可能性【不大】。&#xa;...</title><content type='html'>（接上一单元）&lt;br /&gt;[b]对台湾动武的可能性[/b]&lt;br /&gt;包子是否会对台湾动武？&lt;br /&gt;目前看，可能性【不大】。&lt;br /&gt;（当然，未来可能会出现其它变化，另当别论）&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;为啥俺认为：【目前】可能性不大。&lt;br /&gt;原因有好几个。&lt;br /&gt;最简单的对比就是——&lt;br /&gt;如果朝廷连香港都搞不定，就更不用提——渡海作战了。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;大致对比一下“香港军事戒严”与“武力统一台湾”。&lt;br /&gt;上述这两者，不论是【军事难度】、【国际舆论】、【外交博弈】、【政治风险】。&lt;br /&gt;前者都要【远远小于】后者。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/196160292738312245'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/196160292738312245'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129998129#c196160292738312245' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/7960474635155432338'/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='//4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:59:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4205313350954834473</id><published>2019-10-15T16:58:53.876+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:58:53.876+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO 编程随想&#xa;问题在于中共已经吸取了前苏联和东欧共产党国家解体的经验教训，很难通过非暴力革命方式推...</title><content type='html'>TO 编程随想&lt;br /&gt;问题在于中共已经吸取了前苏联和东欧共产党国家解体的经验教训，很难通过非暴力革命方式推翻政权。由于有维尼这样的废物，像苏联这种自上而下的非暴力革命导致解体，基本上不可能在中国发生。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/4205313350954834473'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/4205313350954834473'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129933876#c4205313350954834473' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/5435637948667885368'/><author><name>AntiCCP</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-773712277"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:58:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3967417903918535210</id><published>2019-10-15T16:56:51.003+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:56:51.003+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO 原教旨自由主义者&#xa;[b]关于“武力统一台湾”[/b]&#xa;俺在评论区与很多读者交流过，随手列几条（...</title><content type='html'>TO 原教旨自由主义者&lt;br /&gt;[b]关于“武力统一台湾”[/b]&lt;br /&gt;俺在评论区与很多读者交流过，随手列几条（链接如下）&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/06/june-fourth-incident-32.html?comment=1529057806850&lt;br /&gt;https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/04/Zhao-at-GitHub.html?comment=1525104088369&lt;br /&gt;https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/02/Constitutional-Amendment.html?comment=1520953810411&lt;br /&gt;https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/02/Constitutional-Amendment.html?comment=1521389181758</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/3967417903918535210'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/3967417903918535210'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129811003#c3967417903918535210' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/7960474635155432338'/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='//4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:56:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8229938011069438167</id><published>2019-10-15T16:53:07.535+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:53:07.535+08:00</updated><title type='text'>有人说到暴力革命，我是不赞同的。在现代社会中，中国乃至全世界，人民和政权之间的武力都是不对等的，中国...</title><content type='html'>有人说到暴力革命，我是不赞同的。在现代社会中，中国乃至全世界，人民和政权之间的武力都是不对等的，中国尤为甚之，暴力革命，你拿什么来暴力革命呢？是义和团的刀枪不入，还是老美的半自动步枪？你什么都没有，你暴力革什么命？“暴力革命说者”请好好研究研究红色高棉&lt;br /&gt;我有几个意见想给大家，让大家也参考参考，共同学习学习。&lt;br /&gt;中国如果要发生革命只有两种可能&lt;br /&gt;自上而下&lt;br /&gt;       由上层所引发的政治革命&lt;br /&gt;由外到内&lt;br /&gt;       由外部压力/支持传导至内部所产生的革命&lt;br /&gt;       如：世界大战&lt;br /&gt;           工业革命&lt;br /&gt;                ...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;所以，大家还是不要抱有暴力革命的念头，于人于己都不好，目前环境下，只有和平演变一条路可走，至于你是祈祷全民民主意识觉醒，还是期待一个民主领导人上台，就看你自己了，那个能让你睡得香就选择那个。&lt;br /&gt;</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/8229938011069438167'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/8229938011069438167'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129587535#c8229938011069438167' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1535543875"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:53:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2306602452433553259</id><published>2019-10-15T16:50:30.326+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:50:30.326+08:00</updated><title type='text'>[quote]&#xa;而且时间越长，你被爆破的风险越大，哪一天你被抓了，大家就彻底失去希望了，我们也没有什...</title><content type='html'>[quote]&lt;br /&gt;而且时间越长，你被爆破的风险越大，哪一天你被抓了，大家就彻底失去希望了，我们也没有什么可以联络的地方了，大家就如同一盘散沙被大风一刮消失在苍茫的大沙漠中&lt;br /&gt;[/quote]</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/2306602452433553259'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/2306602452433553259'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129430326#c2306602452433553259' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/5435637948667885368'/><author><name>AntiCCP</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-773712277"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:50:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3256393278458386999</id><published>2019-10-15T16:46:35.263+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:46:35.263+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO AntiCCP&#xa;为啥俺【反对】暴力革命，已经在[url=https://program-thi...</title><content type='html'>TO AntiCCP&lt;br /&gt;为啥俺【反对】暴力革命，已经在[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2011/12/revolution-0.html]《谈革命》系列博文[/url]其中一篇，聊得很清楚了。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;当然，你完全可以【不赞同】俺的观点。&lt;br /&gt;如果你想要推动【暴力革命】，也是你的自由。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/3256393278458386999'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/3256393278458386999'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129195263#c3256393278458386999' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/5435637948667885368'/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='//4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:46:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1214041161832764177</id><published>2019-10-15T16:46:33.337+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:46:33.337+08:00</updated><title type='text'>[quote]&#xa;如果中共能够撑过22世纪，那我们就真的没什么指望了；我们总说等机会，非暴力革命，战略...</title><content type='html'>[quote]&lt;br /&gt;如果中共能够撑过22世纪，那我们就真的没什么指望了；我们总说等机会，非暴力革命，战略上悲观，战术上乐观，我们总是一直在拖。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;国内的形式越来越严峻，共匪统治的时间越长，民主的难度就越大，倘若几百年后，即使推翻了中共，民众也是变的和脑残一样了，根深蒂固各种余毒恐怕使民主进程根本无法展开。凡是被共产党折腾过的国家没几十年元气很难恢复，有时候需要上百年其阴霾才能消散殆尽，就如同核污染核辐射一样。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;等待机会可以，但要有个期限，给自己个期限，也给别人承诺，这个期限可以很长，但不能一直无止境就这么将就下去，这样的日子真不知道什么时候才是个头。人生有限，短短几十载，真正壮年失去也就二三十年，过了这个阶段，你再想做什么也有心无力了，我们毕竟是肉体之躯，我们都会老去，一定要把握住时间，在有限的时间内让个体产生无限的价值。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;我觉得应该给读者、大家一个期限，不能这么盲目下去。&lt;br /&gt;[/quote]</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/1214041161832764177'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/1214041161832764177'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129193337#c1214041161832764177' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/5435637948667885368'/><author><name>AntiCCP</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-773712277"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:46:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3326642860859258627</id><published>2019-10-15T16:44:17.542+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:44:17.542+08:00</updated><title type='text'>[quote]&#xa;如果往最坏的方面想，那就是雇佣兵，你觉得是否可行呢，佣兵的战斗力是非常强的，十万佣兵...</title><content type='html'>[quote]&lt;br /&gt;如果往最坏的方面想，那就是雇佣兵，你觉得是否可行呢，佣兵的战斗力是非常强的，十万佣兵足以结果共产党。当然这是打算在21世纪末采取的行动，最后的计划，鄙人目前在香港，目前的计划是这样的：&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;1.雇佣兵介入挑起战争，无关输赢，旨在挑起战争，解决欧美国家(尤其是美国)“师出无门”，此举就像一颗手榴弹去炸一火药，干柴烈火一点即爆。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;2.届时，各方面都会支持反共，立场鲜明举起反共大旗，香港、台湾、美国、各新闻报社、人权观察组织、海内外、网络、推特...等等，到时群情激愤，必结果了中共不可，此举做一个引子，旨在动员所有人，核心目的是引起连锁反应。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;3.就算不能成功，中共也肯定会被吓的魂飞魄散，全世界都是倒共之声，中共也名存实亡，过街老鼠人人喊打，在内忧外患之下，此时再进行非暴力革命就如同补刀，一击即倒。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;4.研究中共数十载，已经找到了其几处软肋，只需袭击这几处弱点，中共必会手忙脚乱，惊慌失措，上忙下乱，应接不暇。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;5.我知道随想不喜欢、不希望这样做，但我觉得以你博客的力量未必能在22世纪前终结共产党，希望渺茫到几乎可以不计，你觉得呢？当然，如果能那样做最好，以非暴力革命的方式结束中共，但概率很小，我衷心的希望能如此。&lt;br /&gt;[/quote]</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/3326642860859258627'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/3326642860859258627'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html?showComment=1571129057542#c3326642860859258627' title=''/><link rel='related' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/1295579991922375223/comments/default/5435637948667885368'/><author><name>AntiCCP</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='https://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/10/weekly-share-138.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1295579991922375223' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/1295579991922375223' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-773712277"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2019年10月15日 下午4:44:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-7930330545422662262</id><published>2019-10-15T16:44:16.215+08:00</published><updated>2019-10-15T16:44:16.215+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO 基尔霍夫&#xa;老熟人，好久不见。&#xa;欢迎来捧场 :)&#xa;</title><content type='html'>TO 基尔霍夫&lt;br /&gt;老熟人，好久不见。&lt;br /&gt;欢迎来捧场 :)&lt;br /&gt;</c